
1. Follow the instructions from:

    https://github.com/avin2/SensorKinect

to install the OpenNI binaries, Sensor binaries, the NITE binaries, SDK and Samples

2. Also required is the latest libusb-devel.  Again see instructions from the above
github url.

3. Other helpful:

    http://www.cleoag.ru/2010/12/10/kinect-OpenNi/
    http://www.kinect-hacks.com/kinect-hacks
    https://github.com/OpenNI/OpenNI/tree/unstable
    https://github.com/PrimeSense/Sensor/tree/unstable
    http://www.openni.org/downloadfiles/openni-binaries/20-latest-unstable
